Changelog
=========


1.1
---

 * #2, fixed that the urlbar would not shrink.
 * #1, added possibility to set the padding of the identity icons.
 * Fixed that transitions were not disabled.
 * #4, added ability to disable the animations of the urlbar dropdown.
 * #3, added ability to define a minimum width of the urlbar dropdown.
 * #5, added ability to force the urlbar to a certain height.
 * Tested compatibility with multi-process/e10.


1.0
---

 * Initial release.

